Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥～你到底怎麼了
